  "detailed_description": "20 popular Spider games in one.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDo you love Spider Solitaire (also known as \"Spider\" or \"Spider Patience\"), but want a bigger challenge?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNow you can play Spider Solitaire and other popular variants with different levels of difficulty.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe collection contains:<br />\r\n• Beeswax<br />\r\n• Black Widow<br />\r\n• Curds and Whey<br />\r\n• Mrs. Mop<br />\r\n• Scorpion<br />\r\n• Simple Simon<br />\r\n• Spider<br />\r\n• Spiderette<br />\r\n• Tarantula<br />\r\n• Wasp<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlus 10 more...<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n• Unlimited undo<br />\r\n• Auto complete<br />\r\n• Statistics<br />\r\n• Rules for each game",
